== 爭議 ==
2005年時，[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]時任執行長[[史提夫·賈伯斯|史提夫·賈伯斯]]相當不滿約翰威立出版沒有經過他授權的個人傳記《iCon: Steve Jobs》（台灣中文版書名《i狂人賈伯斯：從另類人生到超酷創新的蘋果風格驅動家》），曾下令所有[[Apple_Store|Apple Store]]禁止販賣約翰威立出版書籍<ref>{{cite news |title=Steve Jobs's Review of His Biography: Ban It |last=Hafner |first=Katie |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=April 30, 2005 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2005/04/30/technology/30apple.html |accessdate=2006-10-16 |archive-date=2015-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150508225234/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/04/30/technology/30apple.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Book giant feels wrath of Jobs |last=Orlowski |first=Andrew |work=[[The_Register|The Register]] |date=27 April 2005 |url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2005/04/27/apple_snubs_wiley/ |accessdate=18 July 2009 |archive-date=2020-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517021747/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2005/04/27/apple_snubs_wiley/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

